     <h2>
      <a href="/">
       mnmlst
      </a>
      :
      <b>
       mnmlsm s jst th strt
      </b>
     </h2>
     <div class="entry">
      <p>
       I rcvd sm crtcsm rcntly tht my mnmlst phlsphy f dwnszng r lvs s t ndvdlstc  sltn. I thnk “hypr-ndvdlstc” ws th trm. (Actlly mst f th crtcsm ws bsd n n tdtd pht I sd  fw yrs g, bt I’ll fcs n th prt tht ntrsts m.)
      </p>
      <p>
       Tht gv m ps t thnk: s t  vld crtcsm? And I thnk, t sm lvls, t s — th mnmlsm I prps (lng wth mny thrs) s smthng w mght dpt n  prsn-t-prsn bss, nd pssbly wn’t b dptd by vryn n scty. And f t sn’t, hs t md  dffrnc?
      </p>
      <p>
       Sr t hs — t th ndvdl ppl wh hv dptd mnmlsm. It cn chng yr lf, fr th bttr, nd tht’s nthng t snz t. Bt wll t chng th wrld? Wll t slv pvrty nd glbl wrmng? Obvsly nt, f t’s nly dptd by  smll nmbr f ppl. Fr t t wrk, t wld hv t b wdsprd.
      </p>
      <p>
       S ys, I hr tht. Bt mst w nly prs sltns tht wll b dptd by vryn ll t nc? If w blv  crs f ctn s bttr fr s s ndvdl ppl nd fr scty s  whl, bt w dbt whthr scty s  whl wll dpt t, shld w shn tht crs f ctn?
      </p>
      <p>
       I dn’t blv s. I thnk tht f  wy f lvng s rght, y shld lv tht wy. If t mks yr lf bttr, thn gd. If t’s dptd by th wrld, vn bttr. W cn’t lt th prblm f gttng wdsprd dptn stp s frm strtng.
      </p>
      <p>
       Tht’s wht mnmlsm s prctcd by ndvdl ppl s, t ts hrt: jst  strt. Scrts sd, “Lt h tht wld mv th wrld, frst mv hmslf.” Gndh sd, “B th chng y wnt t s n th wrld.” I sy, lt’s strt wth rslvs. If w cnnt wlk th pth, hw cn w sk th wrld t wlk t?
      </p>
      <p>
       Onc w hv shwn tht  mnmlst lf s nt nly pssbl, bt  gd thng, t wll bcm  shnng xmpl t thrs. W cn mv thrs wth r vry lvs. As Gndh ls sd, “My lf s my mssg.” Lt yr lf b yr mssg t th wrld, yr xmpl fr  bttr lf, nd lt tht b th strt.
      </p>
      <p>
       Frm sch smll bgnnngs, grt thngs cn b brn.
      </p>
